title: Correction to: Impact of community mask mandates on SARS-CoV-2 transmission in Ontario after adjustment for differential testing by age and sex
content: This is a correction to: Amy Peng, Savana Bosco, Alison E Simmons, Ashleigh R Tuite, David N Fisman, Impact of community mask mandates on SARS-CoV-2 transmission in Ontario after adjustment for differential testing by age and sex, PNAS Nexus, Volume 3, Issue 2, February 2024, pgae065, https://doi.org/10.1093/pnasnexus/pgae065
